text: Trébeurden is a commune. It is found in the region Bretagne in the Côtes-d'Armor department in the west of France. ==Sister cities== Trébeurden is twinned with: * Vâlcelele, Buzău, Romania, since 1989 * Villanuova sul Clisi, Italy, since 2000 * Newton Ferrers, Devon, England, since 2010 Category:Communes in Côtes-d'Armor
title: Trébeurden
